e="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;">- Vous pourrez développer un nouveau canal de vente lucratif </span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;">- Vous aurez la possibilité de vendre rapidement et facilement en Europe et dans le reste du monde</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;">- Vous pouvez créer des annonces et vendre vos objets sur les deux canaux à partir d&#039;un point unique</span><br style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;" /><span style="font-family: arial, sans, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;">- Vous pouvez installer le module eBay sans frais supplémentaires </span></p>					<div class="gamification-tip-infobox-content-controls right">\n						<a href="javascript:$.fancybox.close();" class="button">Annuler</a>\n						<a href="{link}AdminModules{/link}&install=ebay&module_name=ebay" class="button success">Installer le module</a>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<script>\n	$(document).ready( function () {\n		$(''.gamification_fancybox'').bind(''click'', function () {\n			id_advice = 375;\n			popin_url = ''https://gamification.prestashop.com/get_advice_link.php?id_advice=''+id_advice+''&url='';\n			url = window.location.origin+window.location.pathname.replace(''index.php'', '''')+$(''.gamification-tip-infobox-content-controls a.success'').attr(''href'');\n			$(''.gamification-tip-infobox-content-controls a.success'').attr(''href'', popin_url+encodeURIComponent(url));\n			\n			$(''.gamification-tip-infobox'').after(''<img style="display:none" src="https://gamification.prestashop.com/api/getAdvicePopinImg/''+id_advice+''.png" />'');\n			\n		});\n	});\n</script></div>'),
